            <description><![CDATA[【🤧<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%B5%81%E6%84%9F%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E7%AD%89%E7%BA%A7%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳流感风险等级为中#</span></a> 】深圳市疾病风险综合预报结果显示，2月21日至27日深圳流感的风险等级为“中”。目前，流感疫苗是预防流感的有效方式。当前，深圳的社康机构等还可以接种疫苗。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫提醒大家，还需防范流感、登革热、诺如病毒感染等传染病。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5003817750822923" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">第一现场的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6aac5feagy1hn0xnenr72j20u01hc0vg.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/b72CCnZrgx08cHZ5rTfa010412003qCe0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708722209&amp;ssig=WhBnWG7b5N&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/sqzKhhiXgx08cHZ5nymA010412002eL30E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708722209&amp;ssig=GAydzC0SF4&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/5TA0MOssgx08cHZ5ndOo010412001i9b0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1708722209&amp;ssig=OdsZxZ3cRL&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5003817750822923" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
